name: dev-graph
description: node/next/worktree/status/sync/renderの運用ループでlocal graph、tracker projection、worktree lifecycleを管理するlocal-first plugin bundle。
kind: plugin-composition
version: 0.2.0
owner: harness maintainers

contract:
  intent: 確定済みartifactを正規content rootとgraphへatomic登録し、ready計算・worktree lease・状態確認・tracker同期・静的可視化を収束させる。
  interface:
    inputs: [natural-language-want, graph-node, system-spec-import, feature-execution-package]
    outputs: [local-graph, markdown-artifacts, tracker-projections, ready-sets, build-handoff]
  invariant:
    - local graph/Markdownが正本で外部trackerはbinding別projectionである
    - C02だけがgraph/content writerでC12/C28だけが外部tracker writerである
    - public commandはnode/next/worktree/status/sync/renderの6 verbだけを受理する
    - next/statusはgraph/content/tracker/leaseを変更せずeval-logだけを書ける
    - worktree lease正本はgit common dir配下dev-graphであり.dev-graph/locksは使わない
    - C14はmacro featureだけを所有しexact-13 task生成はexternal system-dev-plannerへ委譲する
    - C19はexternal system-spec-harnessを引用しcompilerを複製しない
    - caller repository外content accessとfeature branch上durable completionを拒否する

capabilities:
  - {kind: skill, ref: skills/run-dev-graph-init, tier: core}
  - {kind: skill, ref: skills/run-dev-graph-node, tier: core}
  - {kind: skill, ref: skills/run-dev-graph-sync, tier: core}
  - {kind: skill, ref: skills/run-dev-graph-requirements, tier: core}
  - {kind: skill, ref: skills/run-dev-graph-render, tier: core}
